{"tid":627470,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《小丑回魂2》即將開拍 主演有可能Jessica Chastain配James McAvoy","createTime":"2018-04-13T04:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T23:23:09.000Z","uid":41343,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b4eef0b02f125451fecf11298700d8a32e6f3323","tid":627470,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"繼傑西卡&middot;查斯坦（Jessica Chastain）後，又有一位重量級明星開始商談加盟《小丑回魂2》（IT Chapter 2），他就是我們熟悉的&ldquo;X教授&rdquo;詹姆斯&middot;麥卡沃伊（ James McAvoy）！<br />\n<br />\n據悉，他洽談的角色是比爾（Bill），是&ldquo;失敗者俱樂部&rdquo;（Losers Club）的主角，在第一集裡由Jaeden Lieberher出演。<br />\n<br />\n而傑西卡&middot;查斯坦的角色則是&ldquo;失敗者俱樂部&rdquo;裡唯一的女孩&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;貝芙&rdquo;（Bev），第一集裡這個角色由索菲亞&middot;莉莉絲（Sophia Lillis）飾演。<br />\n<br />\n另外，喜劇演員比爾&middot;哈德（Bill Hader）也在洽談，可能會出演長大後的&ldquo;里奇&rdquo;（Richie），該角色小時候由芬&middot;伍夫哈德（Finn Wolfhard）飾演。<br />\n<br />\n《小丑回魂2》故事發生在首集影片的27年後（也就是現在）。&ldquo;失敗者俱樂部&rdquo;（Losers Club）的孩子們都長大了，陸續離開了小鎮。只有黑人成員麥克（Mike Hanlon）留在了小鎮上當守門人。<br />\n<br />\n麥克成為了圖書管理員，他在當地走訪了解到了關於&ldquo;小丑&rdquo;的很多歷史，並試圖在&ldquo;小丑&rdquo;下次輪迴前找到擊敗他的辦法。麥克成天生活在恐懼和壓力中，只好通過毒品讓自己逃離現實。<br />\n<br />\n續集中，&ldquo;失敗者俱樂部&rdquo;（Losers Club）成員將由一群新的成人演員來飾演，但是小演員們依然會在閃回片段中出現。當然，那個嚇壞大家的&ldquo;小丑&rdquo;不會換人，仍由比爾&middot;斯卡斯加德（Bill Skarsgard）扮演。<br />\n<br />\n《小丑回魂2》計劃2019年9月6日上映，影片仍由安迪&middot;馬提希（Andy Muschietti）導演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/120121_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F120121_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2c30dfd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a2e8583bc36f31970969ebf52ebf2e765e4fb09","tid":627470,"uid":78971,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"James McAvoy 好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6503f2b6704a41a64a7d91c9f9b42499afea3dfd","tid":627470,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"原來當年翻拍果套IT分開左上下集黎拍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW&hellip;&hellip;舊版佢地大個左最後果場決戰好鳩下，希望改改佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4156015500d8c046d254cd153115b7da53de5745","tid":627470,"uid":70800,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a2e8583bc36f31970969ebf52ebf2e765e4fb09","tid":627470,"uid":78971,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"James McAvoy 好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"好正 佢個accent <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f81d2aa9c6de2f83ef701d3276d1dc760c9538f","tid":627470,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/123057_d444c4494abec77b9a1f99a6ce5abc18.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F123057_d444c4494abec77b9a1f99a6ce5abc18.gif&h=b3ecad45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89a5389fc4422842c4cb4bc403c630d4696bccb4","tid":627470,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a2e8583bc36f31970969ebf52ebf2e765e4fb09","tid":627470,"uid":78971,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"James McAvoy 好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"又一次俾Jessica飛"},{"pid":"d32ab46733f9a2e6821541fa6986ceaa540b9966","tid":627470,"uid":17152,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係搵amy adams做成人版bev<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6554b95bbda7903beb55d87f7c37c3dce26dbfb4","tid":627470,"uid":2162,"like":0,"dis